  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "The charged layer where aurora is born. Shimmer feedback at 0.78 with damping pulled to 0.12 allows the high harmonics to ring free -- the reverb tail becomes a self-sustaining luminous curtain. Unison at 5 with minimal detune (0.03) creates interference patterns that shimmer like charged particles. The Tongue says: aftertouch opens the filter from 2400 Hz upward, revealing the full spectrum like sunlight piercing clouds.",
